Percona XtraDB Cluster 8.0
--------------------------

Percona XtraDB Cluster is based on Percona Server and Codership wsrep API
using galera replication library that provides Multimaster Cluster based
on synchronous replication.

https://www.percona.com/software/mysql-database/percona-xtradb-cluster

Documentation: https://www.percona.com/doc/percona-xtradb-cluster/8.0/index.html

Jira (bugs): https://jira.percona.com/projects/PXC/issues

Sources: https://github.com/percona/percona-xtradb-cluster
